        <li><strong>Midjourney v7</strong> wins on out-of-the-box image quality, ease of use, and zero hardware requirements. Best for marketers, hobbyists, and creatives who want cinematic results fast.</li>
        <li><strong>Stable Diffusion 3</strong> wins on control, customization, and cost. Best for developers, technical artists, and teams that need LoRA training, ControlNet, and local or API deployment.</li>
        <li><strong>Pricing:</strong> Midjourney starts at $10/month; Stable Diffusion is free and open source, with optional cloud APIs.</li>
        <li><strong>Verdict:</strong> Pick Midjourney for speed and aesthetics. Pick Stable Diffusion for precision, scale, and budget.</li>
      </ul>
